    "en": {
      "title": "Trains, SLTB buses run as usual, limited private buses",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Even though trains are in operation as usual, buses only take a limited turn owing to unavailability of fuel.",
        "The Railways General Manager (GMR) Dhammika Jayasundara said that all trains, including office trains are on tracks today.",
        "Meanwhile, the private bus owners said they would operate buses as per availability of fuel. However, the Sri Lanka Transport Board (SLTB) said they would operate buses as usual. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
